lichen-gateway/src/gateway.rs:117-148 tests use:
```rust
let schc = gw.upstream_to_mesh(packet).expect("compress failed");
let recovered = gw.mesh_to_upstream(&schc).expect("decompress failed");
```

In test code, .unwrap() is idiomatic; .expect() with generic messages adds noise without improving diagnostics (test failures show the line number anyway). Either use .unwrap() or provide test-specific context.
